data.description:
Discover the charm of country living with the convenience of city amenities in this spacious home that boasts an open one-acre lot all nestled in Lincoln County.

Start your mornings on the covered front porch, while sipping coffee and listening to the serene sounds of nature. Upon entering the home you'll embrace the open foyer and the high vaulted ceilings over the charming family room. This home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, including two master suites each with their own full bathrooms and are conveniently located at opposite ends of the house for added privacy.

As the heart of the home, the kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space and lots of counter space for all your culinary needs. The dining area is perfect for a large country table for family dinners.
 Step outside to the expansive fully fenced backyard where you'll find a fire pit and a small pergola for those who cherish privacy and outdoor activities—ideal for gatherings, BBQs, or simply relaxing in a peaceful setting. The yard has plenty of room for a swing set, pool, garden, or workshop—let your imagination run wild!

Additionally, the property includes an outbuilding for extra storage or projects. Enjoy the feel of country living while being just moments away from grocery stores, shopping centers, dining options, or fishing at the beautiful Lake Thurmond.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a slice of tranquility with endless possibilities in the heart of Lincolnton!
